Starts a IMC transaction. The Start-ImcTransaction cmdlet starts a transaction, which is a series of PowerTool cmdlets that are managed as a unit. A transaction can be completed (CompleteImcTransaction), or it can be completely undone (Undo-ImcTransaction). Because the commands in a transaction are managed as a unit, either all commands are committed or all commands are rolled back.
